                        <interp inst="t18630406-name-130" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE PANGBOURN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Solomons, a pawnbroker in Gray's Inn-lane—I produce a gold chain, pledged by the prisoner on 31st March.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
