                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Smith, a pawnbroker at Islington—I produce a locket pledged by the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoner put in a paper, stating that in consequence of being fifteen months out of employment, he was induced by necessity to commit the offence, but that he had done all he could to facilitate the recovery of the property, and begged for mercy.</hi>—</p>
